('9510166b-d023-4b80-bdc7-69bfa53039e3','Hs 11','L 1068',61.7663,17.0402,'uifostr : lit …sa : s---n þina : abtiʀ : uta : -a-uʀ sin : kuþ hialbi salu honis : þiʀ markaþu : runa : aluiʀ · ak bratr :','"Vifastr let [ræi]sa s[tæi]n þenna æftiʀ "Udda, [f]a[ð]ur sinn. "Guð hialpi salu hans. Þæiʀ markaðu runaʀ, "Alveʀ/"Ølveʀ ok "Brandr.',NULL,'Véfastr had this stone raised in memory of Oddi, his father. May God help his soul. Ǫlvir and Brandr, they marked the runes.',NULL,NULL,'Runsten','Granit','Hälsingland','Sweden'),
('51194bf2-0443-4217-85ad-5fff695985b3','Hs 19','L 1953',61.8135,16.5696,'sia : ma : þu : a · mkh : æi : ma þu : fa : mik : kunnar : kærþi : mik : kirkain : a · mkh : s[æ]luk maria','Sea ma þu a mik, æi ma þu fa mik. "Gunnarr gærði mik. Kirkian a mik. Salug "Maria.',NULL,'You may look at me, you may not get me. Gunnar made me. The church owns me. Blessed Mary.','1200-talet','Enligt uppgift skulle runorna vara påbättrade.','Portring','Järn','Hälsingland','Sweden'),
